# Kids Corner — Meshy API key (build-time asset generation only).
#
# 1) Copy this file to `.env` in the same folder:  cp .env.example .env
# 2) Paste your key from https://www.meshy.ai  →  Settings → API Keys
# 3) `.env` is gitignored — the key never reaches GitHub or the app bundle.
#
# NEVER commit the real key, and never put it in client/src code: the World is
# a static site, so anything in the bundle is public. This key is used ONLY by
# scripts/meshy/generate.mjs on your machine.

MESHY_API_KEY=
